title: East Gongchen Bridge station
text: East Gongchen Bridge () is a <a href="metro%20station">metro station</a> on <a href="Line%205%20%28Hangzhou%20Metro%29">Line 5</a> of the <a href="Hangzhou%20Metro">Hangzhou Metro</a> in China. It is located in the <a href="Gongshu%20District">Gongshu District</a> of Hangzhou.
